abstract: >-
  A Python toolkit for systematic adversarial probing of LLM
  deployments against the OWASP Top 10 for LLM Applications (2025).
  Implements direct and indirect prompt injection payloads, jailbreak
  templates, and an automated scoring harness that reports
  per-vulnerability pass/fail rates with refusal detection. Ships with
  adapters for OpenRouter, NVIDIA NIM, and any OpenAI-compatible
  endpoint, and a Rich-based TUI for live probe execution.
